item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossy)】MP3 - Lady Gaga - ARTPOP (DJ Liiiam's 2023 Non-Stop Mix)
item.description:
To celebrate the 10 year anniversary of one of the most boisterous, chaotic, and joyful albums of the 2010s, ARTPOP, I give you a full remaster and recreation of my original project, ARTPOP (Non-Stop Mix), from 2013. (If any of y'all were on GagaDaily and Tumblr, you may remember the first rendition)

I am very proud of this new version, and I hope it serves you well as you go on celebrating this album for it's 10 year anniversary and beyond! Thanks for tuning in.
